0near%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELecornu%20revealed%20a%20new%20%26quot%3BVery%20High%20Altitude%26quot%3B%20strategy%20in%20June%20for%20France's%20military%2C%20the%20purpose%20being%20to%20detect%20and%20identify%20objects%20maneuvering%20in%20that%2012.4%20to%2062.1%20mile%20altitude%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20includes%20air%20defense%20radars%2C%20new%20long-range%20and%20ultra-high%20frequency%20radars%2C%20and%20satellites%20for%20detection%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Binterception%26quot%3B%20component%20that%20uses%20fighter%20aircraft%20and%20missiles%2C%20according%20to%20France's%20armed%20forces%20ministry.%20France%20is%20also%20looking%20into%20developing%20surface%20lasers%20for%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20balloon%20test%20was%20part%20of%20the%20new%20strategy%2C%20MBDA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMBDA%20described%20the%20altitude%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20increasingly%20contested%20area%20of%20conflict%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday.%20It%20called%20the%20tests%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20they%20%26quot%3Bdemonstrated%20the%20feasibility%20of%20neutralising%20this%20new%20type%20of%20threat.%26quot%3B%20It%20said%20the%20threats%20in%20those%20layers%20of%20the%20atmosphere%20include%20espionage%20and%20surveillance.%20Other%20potential%20threats%20beyond%20balloons%20include%20drones%20and%20hypersonic%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222627%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Rafale%20fighter%20jet%20in%20the%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681cd0b8a466d2b74ab56545%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20French-made%20Rafale%20fighter%20jet.%3Cp%3E(Photo%20by%20Sonu%20Mehta%2FHindustan%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jets%20used%20in%20the%20recent%20test%20were%20both%20French%3A%20Mirage%202000s%20are%20multi-role%2C%20delta-winged%20fourth-