0difficult%20year%20of%20trying%20to%20save%20money%20and%20finally%20letting%20it%20go%2C%20I%20was%20prepared%20to%20give%20up%20and%20never%20develop%20a%20physical%20product%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22538a48f5-750a-44f1-87c2-726015a051b1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%202021%2C%20I%20came%20up%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20smart%20breathing%20trainer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Ftypes-of-asthma%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elifelong%20asthmatic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20no%20tool%2C%20pill%2C%20exercise%2C%20or%20equipment%20worked%20well%20for%20me.%20After%20trying%20many%20things%20to%20soothe%20my%20symptoms%2C%20I%20determined%20the%20best%20way%20was%20respiratory%20muscle%20training%2C%20also%20known%20as%20RMT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20and%20tested%20many%20%26quot%3Bbreathing%20trainer%26quot%3B%20devices.%20I%20found%20all%20of%20them%20to%20be%20bulky%20without%20changeable%20resistance%2C%20aesthetically%20unpleasing%2C%20and%20lacking%20features%20for%20breathing%20instructions%20and%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20created%20a%20blueprint%20of%20all%20the%20refinements%20and%20enhancements%20an%20ideal%20breathing%20trainer%20must%20have%20and%20started%20Oumua%20in%202021.%20It's%20an%20AI-powered%20breathing%20trainer%20that%20assists%20people%20with%20living%20longer%2C%20happier%2C%20and%20better%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOumua%20is%20now%20a%20successful%207-figure%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c2360ae-95f3-45cc-9f74-8d0107b3daf8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20a%20field%20you're%20trying%20to%20get%20into%20is%20undoubtedly%20important%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKnowledge%20also%20helps%20increase%20confidence%20when%20you're%20struggling%20with%20impostor%20syndrome.%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20almost%20everything%20to%20create%20tangible%20products%20that%20people%20would%20want