ryone.%20Pick%20the%20field-accoladed%20experts%20who%20have%20a%20track%20record%20of%20success%20and%20regard%20their%20feedback.%20Ignore%20the%20haters.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETry%20not%20to%20overanalyze%20tasks%20that%20appear%20too%20complicated%20or%20unachievable.%20Fake%20it%20until%20you%20make%20it%20doesn't%20work%20when%20you're%20new%20at%20a%20craft.%20You%20can%20only%20make%20it%20by%20not%20being%20overconfident%20and%20overestimating%20your%20abilities%20but%20by%20adapting%20to%20a%20beginner's%20mindset.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELearn%20to%20be%20comfortable%20when%20things%20are%20uncomfortable%2C%20have%20a%20high%20risk%20tolerance%2C%20and%20move%20forward%20even%20when%20circumstances%20and%20outcomes%20are%20uncertain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224cf63f8a-9d56-4741-9990-2b40a49e21ab%5C%22%3EMy%20PR%20background%20definitely%20helped%20me%20as%20I%20became%20a%20founder%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20experience%20built%20my%20business%20intuition%20and%20served%20as%20the%20catalyst%20for%20my%20own%20metamorphosis%20into%20a%20hardware%20creator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20advise%20against%20leaving%20your%20job%20unless%20you've%20saved%20enough%20to%20take%20this%20action.%20Before%20I%20quit%20my%20PR%20job%2C%20I%20had%20about%20six%20months'%20worth%20of%20my%20salary%20to%20develop%20my%20concept%20into%20a%20practical%20prototype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20intended%20to%20create%20a%20medical%20device%20that%20could%20diagnose%2C%20prevent%2C%20and%20even%20cure%2C%20this%20second%20tech%20gadget%20was%20twice%20as%20difficult%20to%20construct.%20Oumua%20has%20five%20more%20noninvasive%20medical%20devices%20in%20the%20research%20and%20development%20and%20prototyping%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20do%20you%20think%20you%20are%3F%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20first%20question%20you%20ask%20yourself%20every%20morning%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20highly%20specialized%20degree%20needed%20for%20a%20certain%20product.%20The%20ke