t%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%20verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20TV%20court%20coverage%20blaring%20and%20her%20X%20feed%20scrolling%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she%20greeted%20his%20acquittals%20as%20very%20good%20news%20for%20her%20own%20high-profile%20sex%20trafficking%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20initial%20reaction%20was%20that%20the%20jury%20got%20it%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%2C%20attorney%20for%20luxury%20real%20estate%20broker%20Tal%20Alexander%2C%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexander-brothers-arrested-miami-real-estate-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethree%20Alexander%20brothers%20charged%20with%20sex%20trafficking%20conspiracy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Alexanders'%20case%20is%20set%20for%20trial%20in%20January.%20It%20will%20be%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice's%20next%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsean-diddy-combs-businesses-net-worth-verdict-lawsuit-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebig%20celebrity%20sex-trafficking%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20same%20courthouse%20as%20Combs'%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Alexander%20brothers%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexander-brothers-sex-trafficking-real-estate-agents-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETal%20and%20Oren%20were%20luxury%20brokers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Miami%20and%20Manhattan%2C%20and%20Alon%20was%20an%20executive%20at%20his%20family's%20private%20security%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20operated%20a%20long-running%20sex%20trafficking%20scheme%2C%20the%20government%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20verdict%20like%20this%20is%20refreshing%20and%20it's%20heartening%20because%20it%20means%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-trial-jury-sean-combs-sex-trafficking-racketeering-partial-verdict-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20jury%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20its%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Paul%2C%20a%20former%20New%20York%20City%20prosecutor%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mugshots%20of%20Alon%2C%20Oren%2C%20and%20Tal%20Alexander%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68704bc785e81483682dcf8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Alexander%20brothers%20were%20indicted%20on%20federal%20sex%20trafficking%20charges.%3Cp%3EDepartment%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20followed%20the%20Combs%20trial%20closely%20as%20an%20expert%20commentator%20for%20a%20range%20of%20outlets%2C%20including%20Fox%20News%20and%20MSNBC.%20She%20is%20part%20of%20a%20defense%20team%20that%20now%20considers%20the%20Combs%20verdict%20as%20proof%20that%20a%20federal%20jury%20in%20Manhattan%20can%20see%20past%20the%20raw%20emotion%20of%20a%20sex%20trafficking%20case%20and%20find%20that%20the%20evidence%2C%20heart-wrenching%20though%20it%20might%20be%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-verdict-feds-overreached-racketeering-charge-mob-boss-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edoes%20not%20fit%20the%20law.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers'%20lawyers%20say%20that%20in%20their%20case%2C%20that%20misfitting%20of%20the%20evidence%20to%20the%20law%20stems%20in%20large%20part%20from%20a%20single%20word%20in%20the%20federal%20sex-trafficking%20statute%3A%20%26quot%3BCommercial.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%202024%20indictment%20accuses%20the%20three%20of%20conspiring%20to%20cause%20at%20least%20six%20female%20victims%20to%20cross%20state%20lines%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20commercial%20sex%20acts%2C%20meaning%20assaults%20and%20rapes%20stretching%20back%20to%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%2C%20acting%20%26quot%3Bsometimes%20alone%20and%20sometimes%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20drugged%20the%20women%20or%20physically%20held%20them%20down%20before%20violating%20them%2C%20the%20indictment%20says.%20The%20victims%20include%20one%20woman%20who%20was%20a%20minor%20at%20the%20time%2C%20prosecutors%20also%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20were%20these%20%26quot%3Bcommercial%26quot%3B%20sex%20acts%2C%20as%20the%20federal%20sex-trafficking%20law%20requires%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20prosecutors%20say.%20The%20indictment%20alleges%20that%20the%20three%20brothers%20lured%20their%20victims%20using%20%26quot%3Bmaterial%20benefits%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20luxury%20parties%20and%20events%20with%20commercial%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Combs%20case%2C%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bcommercial%26quot%3B%20was%20not%20in%20dispute.%20Federal%20prosecutors%20alleged%20that%20Combs%20paid%20male%20escorts%20to%20cross%20state%20lines%20and%20have%20sex%20with%20his%20girlfriends%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-trial-different-rapper-hosted-freak-off-las-vegas-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eas%20he%20watched%20and%20filmed%20them%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20no%20cash%20transactions%20or%20prostitution%20alleged%20in%20the%20Alexander%20brothers'%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20to%20quote%20from%20the%20indictment%2C%20the%20victims%20were%20lured%20to%20their%20sexual%20assaults%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20%26quot%3Bdomestic%20and%20international%20travel%20to%20vacation%20destinations%2C%20luxury%20accommodations%20at%20high-end%20hotels%20and%20vacation%20properties%2C%20and%20access%20to%20other%20luxury%20experiences%20and%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20interpretation%20of%20commercial%20sex%20acts%20%26quot%3Bwould%20effectively%20federalize%20any%20type%20of%20date%20rape%26quot%3B%20involving%20gifts%20and%20interstate%20travel%2C%20argues%20Jason%20Goldman%2C%20who%20is%20repping%20all%20three%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20perpetrator%20met%20a%20woman%20on%20a%20dating%20app%2C%20invited%20her%20to%20dinner%2C%20paid%20for%20the%20dinner%2C%20and%20then%20sexually%20assaulted%20her%20later%20that%20night%2C%20it%20would%20constitute%20sex%20trafficking%20under%20the%20government's%20theory%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20wrote%20last%20month%20in%20a%20filing%20seeking%20to%20dismiss%20the%20indictment's%20sex%20trafficking%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20entirely%20novel%20and%20untested%20criminal%20theory%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20aware%20of%20no%20indictment%20charging%20sex%20trafficking%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20'promises%20of%20luxury%20experiences%2C%20travel%2C%20and%20accommodations'%20%E2%80%94%20i.e.%2C%20a%20weekend%20invitation%20to%20a%20summer%20beach%20house%20and%20the%20means%20to%20get%20there%E2%80%94provide%20the%20'commercial'%20basis%20for%20a%20sex%20trafficking%20charge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bcausal%26quot%3B%20connection%20between%20the%20thing%20of%20value%20and%20what%20happened%20next%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20a%20quid-pro-quo%20where%20something%20is%20exchanged%20between%20individuals%20for%20sex%2C%20he%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20causal%20connection%20is%20absent%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%20trio%20of%20federal%20appellate%20judges%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexander-brothers-denied-bail-contentious-hearing-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edenied%20bail%20for%20the%20brothers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20not%20before%20one%20voiced%20skepticism%20that%20there's%20anything%20akin%20to%20a%20commercial%20sex%20act%20in%20the%20prosecution's%20theory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20US%20Attorney's%20Office%20in%20Manhattan%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20case%20beyond%20the%20prosecution's%20court%20filings.%20The%20government%20is%20due%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20motion%20for%20dismissal%20by%20Thursday%2C%20and%20may%20well%20argue%20that%20this%20causal%20connection%20is%20not%20only%20present%2C%20but%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%2C%20luxury%20accommodations%2C%20and%20travel%20perks%20were%20essentially%20elaborately%20planned%20bait%2C%20the%20indictment%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%20in%20advance%20of%20these%20attacks%2C%20the%20brothers%20and%20their%20friends%20%26quot%3Bshared%20photographs%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20to%20select%20those%20they%20found%20sufficiently%20attractive%20to%20invite%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20parties%20and%20events%20where%20they%20would%20be%20attacked%2C%20the%20indictment%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20defendants%20and%20other%20men%20attending%20the%20trips%20pooled%20financial%20resources%20in%20order%20to%20pay%20for%20flights%20and%20other%20travel%20expenses%20for%20the%20women%20and%20girls%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20indictment%20also%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20up%20to%20a%20jury%2C%20ultimately%2C%20to%20decide%20if%20gifts%20such%20as%20plane%20travel%2C%20event%20invitations%2C%20and%20what%20prosecutors%20call%20offers%20of%20%26quot%3Bluxury%20experiences%26quot%3B%20fit%20the%20definition%20of%20commercial%20sex%20acts%2C%20a%20term%20originally%20meant%20to%20describe%20prostitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20sex%20trafficking%20statute%20is%20a%20powerful%20tool%2C%20said%20Megan%20Lundstrom%2C%20CEO%20of%20Polaris%2C%20which%20advocates%20for%20sex-%20and%20labor-trafficking%20victims%20and%20operates%20the%20National%20Human%20Trafficking%20Hotline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Lundstrom%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20statute%20%26quot%3Bwould%20benefit%20from%20clearer%20language%20around%20modern%20forms%20of%20psychological%2C%20emotional%2C%20and%20financial%20coercion%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20abuses%20of%20trust%20and%20authority%20alleged%20in%20the%20Combs%20and%20Alexander%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCases%20like%20these%20reveal%20not%20a%20stretch%20of%20prosecutorial%20power%2C%20but%20rather%20how%20limited%20the%20public's%20understanding%20of%20trafficking%20still%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Lundstrom%20added%2C%20saying%20that%20often%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20happens%20within%20families%2C%20in%20intimate%20relationships%2C%20and%20under%20the%20undue%20influence%20of%20power%20or%20celebrity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20the%20three%20brothers%20say%20the%20government's%20case%20is%20based%20on%20uncorroborated%20victim%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20indictment%2C%20and%20vehemently%20deny%20the%20allegations%20within%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20told%20BI%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20last%20week's%20Combs%20verdict%2C%20which%20acquitted%20Combs%20of%20sex%20trafficking%20and%20racketeering%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20resounding%20rejection%20of%20the%20government's%20sex%20trafficking%20theory%2C%26quot%3B%20consistent%20with%20the%20government-overreach%20arguments%20in%20last%20month's%20dismissal%20motions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20are%20next%20due%20in%20court%20on%20August%2019%2C%20with%20a%20trial%20date%20set%20for%20January%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexander-brothers-diddy-sex-trafficking-acquittal-good-news-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752224402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68704ee13d5881a51c1d206b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexander-brothers-diddy-sex-trafficking-acquittal-good-news-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lawyers%20for%20luxury%20brokers%20Tal%20and%20Oren%20Alexander%20and%20brother%20Alon%20say%20the%20verdict%20shows%20a%20jury%20can%20see%20beyond%20the%20emotion%20of%20a%20sex-trafficking%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%2