ility%20to%20run%20a%20good%20sales%20process%2C%20keep%20track%20of%20outbounds%20to%20new%20investors%2C%20and%20continuously%20develop%20a%20new%20pipeline%20of%20potential%20investors.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20people%20who%20can%20sell%20to%20investors%20and%20win%20meetings%20without%20a%20preexisting%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Steele%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20sales%20process%20in%20institutional%20fundraising%20is%20very%20long%2C%20and%20somebody%20has%20to%20be%20comfortable%20and%20thrive%20in%20that%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294857759-3566-468a-bc8c-72f75df651ee%5C%22%3EPrivate%20wealth%20%26quot%3Barmy%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20institutional%20fundraising%20dries%20up%2C%20more%20private%20equity%20firms%20are%20launching%20products%20they%20can%20sell%20to%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20%E2%80%94%20a%20trend%20started%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-starwood-real-estate-breit-sreit-investors-withdrawals-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlackstone%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJensen%20Partners'%20data%20shows%20that%20demand%20for%20professionals%20who%20can%20sell%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretail-investors-private-equity-debt-market-401k-liquidity-moodys-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealternative%20investments%20to%20private%20wealth%20channels%3C%2Fa%3E%20jumped%2040%25%20last%20year%20over%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelling%20to%20wealthy%20people%20is%20different%20from%20institutional%20fundraising.%20These%20products%20often%20need%20to%20be%20greenlit%20at%20the%20firm%20level%20before%20fundraisers%20can%20even%20begin%20persuading%20individual%20wealth%20advisors%20to%20pitch%20them%20to%20their%20clients.%20Both%20Steele%20and%20Jensen%20said%20it%20can%20take%20an%20%26quot%3Barmy%26quot%3B%20of%20fundraisers%20to%20be%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20institutional%20fundraisers%2C%20firms%20are%20looking%20for%20professionals%20with%20proven%20experience%20and%20comfort%20with%20the%20process%2C%20which%20tends%20to%20move%20more%20quickly%20than%20institutional%20fundraising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20private%20wealth%2C%20you're%20in%20a%20world%20where%20they're%20executing%20and%20closing%20much%20more%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20Steele%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20firms%20are%20adopting%20a%20sales%20model%20popular%20among%20traditional%20asset%20managers%3A%20the%20external%2Finternal%20approach%2C%20Steele%20said.%20In%20this%20setup%2C%20externals%20handle%20field%20sales%2C%20while%20internals%20support%20from%20the%20office%2C%20including%20by%20supplying%20key%20sales%20information%20to%20the%20externals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a4adcda-797b-4a17-b531-c5e776a24c94%5C%22%3ETalk%20like%20an%20investor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvestor%20relations%20professionals%20are%20in%20high%20demand%20because%20they%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20fundraising.%20Once%20the%20investor%20is%20onboarded%2C%20they%20take%20over%20the%20relationship%2C%20keeping%20fund%20investors%2C%20known%20as%20LPs%20or%20limited%20partners%2C%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20right%20IR%20team%20can%20mean%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20bigger%20check%20at%20the%20next%20fundraising%20round%20%E2%80%94%20or%20no%20check%20at%20all%2C%20recruiters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20is%20increasingly%20demanding%2C%20said%20Anthony%20Keizner%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Odyssey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLPs%20want%20more%20frequent%20updates%20about%20their%20investments%20as%20they%20answer%20to%20their%20own%20stakeholders%2C%26quot%3B%20Keizner%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20might%20want%20to%20know%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20effects%20on%20their%20investment%20from%20macro%20environment%20changes%20like%20tariff%20policies%20or%20a%20Fed%20rate%20cut.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJensen%20said%20she%20is%20also%20seeing%20demand%20for%20professionals%20who%20work%20with%20investors%20at%20the%20capital%20formation%20stage%2C%20making%20sure%20investments%20are%20structured%20to%20the%20LPs'%20liking%20and%20acting%20as%20a%20de-facto%20portfolio%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20referred%20to%20them%20as%20strategic%20account%20development%20or%20strategic%20partnership%20professionals%20and%20said%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20senior%20executives%20with%20deft%20communication%20skills%2C%20acting%20as%20translators%20between%20their%20investment%20team%20and%20the%20LP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20an%20LP's%20perspective%2C%20you%20need%20a%20point%20of%20contact%20that%20can%20sit%20and%20talk%20toe-to-toe%20with%20the%20CIO%2C%26quot%3B%20Jensen%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20need%20to%20know%20exactly%20what%20risks%20the%20CIO%20is%20prepared%20to%20take%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20and%20communicate%20how%20they%20should%20structure%20investments%20around%20their%20portfolio.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224af3e4fd-daea-4750-b9f3-c6916a342f16%5C%22%3ETransferable%20skills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiters%20said%20their%20clients%20are%20looking%20for%20sure%20bets%20%E2%80%94%20or%20what%20Xu%20called%20%26quot%3Bsomeone%20who's%20plug-and-play.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20rising%20demand%20for%20these%20roles%2C%20however%2C%20some%20employers%20have%20become%20increasingly%20open%20to%20candidates%20with%20transferable%20skills%20and%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20might%20have%20sat%20on%20the%20investment%20side%2C%20decided%20you%20have%20the%20DNA%20of%20a%20salesperson%2C%20and%20made%20the%20pivot%2C%26quot%3B%20Jensen%20said.%20People%20with%20backgrounds%20in%20consulting%20have%20also%20been%20known%20to%20make%20the%20pivot%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20private%20wealth%20side%2C%20firms%20have%20considered%20candidates%20in%20sales%20