0asset-backed%20finance%20or%20direct%20lending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20also%20mean%20having%20expertise%20in%20a%20specific%20style%20of%20LP%2C%20like%20insurance.%20One%20in-demand%20role%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapollo-global-single-biggest-opportunity-growth-retirement-athene-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehead%20of%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20usher%20more%20insurance%20capital%2C%20especially%20for%20credit%20funds%20that%20use%20that%20money%20to%20make%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20private%20equity%20firm%20decides%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20develop%20a%20credit%20business%2C%20they're%20most%20likely%20going%20to%20hire%20a%20person%20or%20team%20that's%20focused%20on%20credit%20fundraising%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bill%20Matthews%2C%20partner%20at%20BraddockMatthewsBarrett.%20%26quot%3BThe%20generalist%20model%20doesn't%20work%20so%20well%20when%20you're%20developing%20different%20business%20models.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-careers-fundraising-investor-relations-skills-experiences-jobs-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752224401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686e8260f748d8c055f54095%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-careers-fundraising-investor-relations-skills-experiences-jobs-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Private%20equity%20fundraising%20has%20fallen%20on%20tough%20times%2C%20driving%20demand%20for%20these%20jobs%2C%20skills%2C%20and%20experiences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22anicoll%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Nicoll)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-careers-fundraising-investor-relations-skills-experiences-jobs-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%