cal%3B%20the%20aroma%20of%20fresh%20bakes%20wafts%20out%20from%20every%20second%20store%2C%20tempting%20you%20to%20make%20a%20detour%20and%20grab%20a%20bite%20before%20you%20head%20on%20your%20way.%20Heed%20the%20temptation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20%E2%80%98Elloras%E2%80%99%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20coffee%20and%20a%20bun%20that%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20ditching%20your%20agenda%20for%2C%20but%20also%20a%20great%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%201953%2C%20the%20bakery%20has%20lived%20on%20Rajpur%20Road%20for%20so%20long%20it%E2%80%99s%20become%20one%20with%20the%20landscape.%20As%20the%20third%20generation%2C%20Drona%20Gulati%20(34)%20and%20Mudit%20Gulati%20(36)%2C%20who%20are%20taking%20their%20legacy%20forward%2C%20share%2C%20the%20bakery%20was%20the%20brainchild%20of%20their%20grandfather%2C%20Shri%20Krishan%20Lal%20Gulati%2C%20who%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20before%20opting%20for%20retirement.%20When%20Gulati%20landed%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20it%20was%20as%20a%20refugee%2C%20the%20eldest%20of%20five%20siblings%20who%20had%20just%20lost%20their%20father.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F227895%2Findia-best-bakeries-iconic-kayani-pune-kolkata-nahoum-glenary-wengers-delhi-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20bakery%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20his%20attempt%20at%20eking%20out%20a%20living%2C%20never%20fathoming%20that%20it%20would%20one%20day%20gain%20such%20an%20important%20place%20in%20the%20town%E2%80%99s%20memory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrona%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20had%20two%20brothers.%20One%20of%20them%20dealt%20in%20daily%20items%20like%20milk%2C%20cold%20drinks%2C%20juices%20and%20FMCG.%20The%20other%20brother%20was%20into%20retail%20garments%20and%20shawls.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%20