e%20in%20starting%20a%20bakery%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20Elloras%20was%20born.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBYOB%20(bake%20your%20own%20bread)%20%26amp%3B%20some%20wood-fire%20magic%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInteresting%20to%20note%20is%20that%20all%20Elloras%20outlets%20are%20in%20Dehradun%20%E2%80%94%20the%20no-preservative%20policy%20necessitates%20that%20bakes%20must%20be%20consumed%20within%20their%20natural%20shelf%20life.%20But%2C%20beyond%20the%20bakeries%20too%2C%20Drona%20says%2C%20Elloras%E2%80%99%20products%20are%20making%20inroads%20into%20Uttarakhand%20and%20northern%20India.%20These%20outlets%20were%20set%20up%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F405906%2Fcrustworthy-gourmet-breads-pune-startup-jay-panchpor-challah-sourdough%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eburgeoning%20demand%20for%20buns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20rusk%2C%20biscuits%20and%20cookies.%20If%20you%20bite%20into%20an%20Elloras%E2%80%99%20bread%20or%20biscuit%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20guaranteed%20difference%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20able%20to%20pinpoint%2C%20Drona%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20because%20we%20bake%20in%20wood-fired%20ovens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%3B%20mechanisation%20is%20minimal%2C%20and%20quality%20is%20of%20prime%20importance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Felloras-legendary-bakery-dehradun-1-1751639224.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elloras%20outlets%20were%20set%20up%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20burgeoning%20demand%20for%20buns%2C%20rusk%2C%20biscuits%20and%20cookies%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Felloras-legendary-bakery-dehradun-1-1751639224.jpg%201200