gs%20she%20could%20truly%20call%20her%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Kaushalya%20earns%20about%20Rs%205%2C000%20a%20month.%20It%20may%20not%20sound%20like%20much%20to%20some%2C%20but%20for%20her%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20time%20she%E2%80%99s%20had%20money%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20ask%20for.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20an%20income%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20bought%20my%20son%20a%20school%20bag%20with%20my%20own%20money.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20ask%20anyone.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20proud%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20like%20Kaushalya%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20about%20big%20business%20or%20becoming%20entrepreneurs%20overnight.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20small%2C%20steady%20financial%20freedom%3B%20the%20kind%20that%20brings%20real%20choices%20into%20their%20homes.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20being%20able%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20school%20bag%2C%20buy%20vegetables%20without%20permission%2C%20save%20a%20little%20on%20the%20side%2C%20and%20finally%20know%2C%20without%20doubt%2C%20that%20their%20work%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20centre%2C%20women%20who%20were%20once%20told%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20manage%20are%20now%20managing%20just%20fine.%20They%20set%20their%20own%20pace.%20They%20choose%20how%20they%20learn.%20They%20decide%20what%20comes%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-08T172706.076-1751976129.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%20200%20women%20have%20received%20training%20from%20the%20Delhi%20centre%20of%20SAHAS.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-08T172706.076-1751976129.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A